

=Bio=

"Jamie Klinger is working on real-world peer-to-peer based solutions for our global economic woes through the generation of his novel idea, the Jack of all Trade Universe (JoatU).  The concept mixes an exchange-based economy with a community currency generated through a direct-democracy practice.  The currency-generation is done only for the benefit of the community so it is self-perpetuating and self-sustaining."


